org.cougaar.core.agent
Class AgentManager

java.lang.Object
  org.cougaar.util.GenericStateModelAdapter
      org.cougaar.core.component.ContainerSupport
          org.cougaar.core.agent.AgentManager
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Iterable, java.util.Collection, AgentContainer, Component, Container, StateObject, GenericStateModel
public class AgentManager
extends ContainerSupport
implements AgentContainer

A container for Agents.

Although the AgentManager can hold Components other than Agents, the default BinderFactory will only actually accept Agents and other Binders. If you want to load other sorts of components into AgentManager, you'll need to supply a Binder which knows how to bind your Component class.
